# InfoSec Black Friday Deals (OLD)
These were key deals last year, so keep an eye out and update if released.
All the deals for InfoSec related software/tools this Black Friday / Cyber Monday, for all the hackers that saved $$$ during lockdowns.

The below deals have either publicly announced they'll be doing a deal or highly expected.
- All USD
- All End times in UTC
- Do-Your-Own-Research and At-Your-Own-Risk
- There are **NO** referral/affiliate/commission links here

## FAQ
### When do these sales end?
Most end 30th November

### When will most of the deals/discounts be here?
Most likely 26th midday for USA, but deals being added all the time.

### Can I add deals to the page?
Yes, please follow formatting guidelines, provide a source and code. Has to be infosec related, no affiliate links.

:see_no_evil: means 1) Limited to first x users 2) Great deal or 3) Highly recommended by moi

*Disclaimer: I have included my own, and other discount codes sent in directly by DM/Pigeon/Smoke signals.

